OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1777302667
OL,3,CBaby killed in suspected dog attack in
OL,4,CRedcar named at inquest
OL,6,FA baby girl who died following a
OL,7,Fsuspected dog attack at a house in
OL,8,FRedcar has been named, an inquest has
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FMaggie May Ann Moody died at James
OL,12,FCook University Hospital in
OL,13,FMiddlesbrough following an incident at
OL,14,Fa house on Hardale Grove in
OL,15,FDormanstown on 9 April.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
