OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1777302667
OL,3,CBaby killed in suspected dog attack in
OL,4,CRedcar named at inquest
OL,6,FUpon arrival at the scene, armed
OL,7,Fofficers destroyed a dog on the street
OL,8,Fand later destroyed another dog
OL,9,Flocated at the property. Both dogs
OL,10,Fwere assessed and deemed not to be a
OL,11,Fprohibited type of dog by a specialist
OL,12,Fofficer .
OL,14,FThe inquest at Middlesbrough Town Hall
OL,15,Fheard how Maggie was born in Newcastle
OL,16,Fon 10 January and was just one day
OL,17,Faway from turning three months old.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
