OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1777302667
OL,3,CBaby killed in suspected dog attack in
OL,4,CRedcar named at inquest
OL,6,FPaul Appleton, area coroner for
OL,7,FTeesside and Hartlepool, said "At
OL,8,F1.33pm on April 9, 2026, Cleveland
OL,9,FPolice force received a 999 call from
OL,10,Fthe ambulance service reporting they
OL,11,Frequired assistance with an incident,
OL,12,Fin Hardale Grove in Redcar.
OL,14,F"(They were) responding to a child not
OL,15,Fbreathing and the child had been
OL,16,Fattacked by a dog.
OL,26,@vD@BpmvD@Lpn
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1777302667
OL,3,CBaby killed in suspected dog attack in
OL,4,CRedcar named at inquest
OL,6,F"The ambulance service provided
OL,7,Finstructions via the telephone on how
OL,8,Fto provide CPR until emergency service
OL,9,Fworkers arrived. I'm told there were
OL,10,Ftwo dogs present at the address, which
OL,11,Fwas on Hardale Grove.
OL,13,F"Initial accounts provided to my
OL,14,Fofficer have indicated that the dogs
OL,15,Fwere originally in the rear garden but
OL,16,Fthen made their way into the room
OL,17,Fwhere Maggie was located."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1777302667
OL,3,CBaby killed in suspected dog attack in
OL,4,CRedcar named at inquest
OL,6,FA provisional medical cause of death
OL,7,Fwas given as a "head injury",
OL,8,Ffollowing a post-mortem. The three-
OL,9,Fmonth old was identified by her
OL,10,Fgrandmother two days after her death.
OL,12,FThree people have been arrested in
OL,13,Fconnection with the incident. A 45-
OL,14,Fyear-old man was arrested on suspicion
OL,15,Fof being in charge of a dog
OL,16,Fdangerously out of control causing
OL,17,Finjury resulting in death. He was
OL,18,Fsubsequently released on conditional
OL,19,Fbail following questioning.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1777302667
OL,3,CBaby killed in suspected dog attack in
OL,4,CRedcar named at inquest
OL,6,FPolice later confirmed that a 31 year
OL,7,Fold woman was arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fchild neglect and being in charge of a
OL,9,Fdog dangerously out of control
OL,10,Fresulting in death.
OL,12,FA 36 year old man was also arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of being in charge of a dog
OL,14,Fdangerously out of control resulting
OL,15,Fin death. Both have since been
OL,16,Freleased on conditional bail.
OL,18,FNeither of those arrested are
OL,19,Fconnected to the family.
OL,21,FThe inquest was adjourned.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
